snippet.title: Kingdoms Reborn - Trailer | City-builder with Multiplayer and Open World
snippet.description:
Kingdoms Reborn is an open-world city builder with multiplayer. 

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1307890/Kingdoms_Reborn/

Early Access Release on November 3, 2020

The game features challenging resource management combined with an extensive tech tree and upgrades. With multiplayer, you can cooperate or compete in real-time with your friends in the same open world.
